{"tid":1980213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"連儂牆留言：香港人加油","createTime":"2020-04-20T02:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T12:48:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"58f02ffe803fdcf4fbd0c9d644c6c51deea7207f","tid":1980213,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:56:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200420/ER2QMXNPRTABNVBPO7E5R2VISA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200420%2FER2QMXNPRTABNVBPO7E5R2VISA%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=bb1b8f0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200420%2FER2QMXNPRTABNVBPO7E5R2VISA%2F&h=7076937e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200420/ER2QMXNPRTABNVBPO7E5R2VISA/</a><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆留言：香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200420/large/1587314265_d29b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200420%2Flarge%2F1587314265_d29b.gif&h=56bf28de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者點了白汁吞拿魚意粉，點餐後的發票印着港人耳熟能詳的「光復香港」字句。<br />\n<br />\n「保護傘」餐廳開張首日低調而安靜，吸引到不少客人在門外排隊，有市民用膳後在餐廳內的連儂牆留言，希望在香港的手足們平平安安；有人遲來一步捧場落空，也寫下加油小卡，貼在店內的小小連儂牆，留下的一字一句對港人再熟悉不過：「香港人加油！光復香港，時代革命！」<br />\n<br />\n單據印「光復香港」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：多國關注 「與港人同陣線」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果》記者昨日在餐廳點菜後，拿到的發票與單據也印着「光復香港，時代革命，五大訴求，缺一不可」。記者點了「奶油鮪魚意大利麵（白汁吞拿魚意粉）」，雖然等待了一段時間，但餐點並不馬虎，口感十足；不到下午3時，不少菜式都已經售罄，有客人用餐後，在連儂牆寫下：「好榮幸做第一批客人，希望保護傘平平安安，繼續做一眾在台手中（足）嘅保護傘，願榮光，歸香港。」<br />\n<br />\n早在餐廳開張前幾天，許多打算前來捧場的港人撲空，一位以投資移民方式赴台的港人陳女士說，來台灣以後才知道這邊的好，打算長期居留，但轉了念頭又在想，香港現在情況如此差，「我又怎麼放心的下？」<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"c713b8ecf78cc00fd957cd8125f63d269c557adb","tid":1980213,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0fa509a061e9f6bcd4bf23fedf70d7a8565272","tid":1980213,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:48:10.000Z","msg":"台保護傘餐廳開業 食客排長龍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1980803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1980803</a>"}]}